command_group: az aosm publisher artifact-store artifact version

commands.name: az aosm publisher artifact-store artifact version list
commands.syntax:
az aosm publisher artifact-store artifact version list --artifact-name
                                                       --artifact-store-name
                                                       --publisher-name
                                                       --resource-group
                                                       [--max-items]
                                                       [--next-token]
examples: az aosm publisher artifact-store artifact version list --resource-group contoso-aosm --publisher-name contoso --artifact-store-name contoso --artifact-name nginx

commands.name: az aosm publisher artifact-store artifact version update-state
commands.summary: Update artifact state defined in artifact store.
commands.syntax:
az aosm publisher artifact-store artifact version update-state --artifact-name
                                                               [--artifact-state {Active, Deprecated, Preview, Unknown}]
                                                               [--artifact-store-name]
                                                               [--ids]
                                                               [--name]
                                                               [--no-wait {0, 1, f, false, n, no, t, true, y, yes}]
                                                               [--publisher-name]
                                                               [--resource-group]
                                                               [--subscription]
examples: az aosm publisher artifact-store artifact version update-state --resource-group contoso-aosm --publisher-name contoso --artifact-store-name contoso --artifact-name nginx --name 1.0.0 --artifact-state Deprecated
